1601	% These five lemmas decompose the step-(iii) obligation of
1602	% lem:base_change_mate_fstar_reindex_legs (the mate-unwinding crux) into one
1603	% mathematical move each. They are adjoint-mate calculus over the proved
1604	% change-of-rings dictionaries; there is no external source. Composites
1605	% are read left to right, as elsewhere in this chapter.
